Section 3 – License Conditions  
1. Attribution—If You Share the Licensed Material (including in adapted form), You must:  
  a. Provide the name of the creator(s) of the Licensed Material, a copyright notice, a notice that refers to this Public License, a notice that refers to the disclaimer of warranties, and a URI or hyperlink to the Licensed Material.  
